            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1) Open the ui.FormValidator demo in Opera (9.64 or newer on XP or Linux): http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/demobrowser/index.html#ui~FormValidator.html
2) Click one of the text fields to focus it
3) Click &quot;Send&quot;
4) Close the alert box

Expected result:
The text field should lose the focus, i.e. the text input cursor should disappear.

Observed result:
The focus indicator border is removed and the placeholder text is restored but the text cursor remains in the field. Typing anything causes the text to be displayed in grey with the placeholder on top of it.</thetext>
